Package: ranthropicR
Title: R Interface to Anthropic Claude AI Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Pedro", "Emanuel", email = "dr.pedroemanuel@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an R interface to Anthropic's Claude AI models with support for
    text generation and chat-based interactions. Includes functions for model selection,
    parameter customization, and a convenient RStudio addin for interactive use.(Created with Claude Sonnet 3.7).
